title: Prime Jeffries Point 1+ bed with laundry in unit & modern kitchen! 9/1
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 114157763', 'Rent: $2,500 / Month', 'Beds: 1+', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 09/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats & Small Dogs Only', 'Parking:: street parking', 'Renovated apartment with washer & dryer, high ceilings all in a great location.', 'The unit can work as a 2bed, one room is smaller than the other.', 'There is a modern kitchen with updated cabinets, granite countertops & stainless steel appliances, hardwood floors throughout entire apartment, AND Laundry in unit.', 'There is resident permit parking on the street as well as a 5 minute walk to Maverick Station for blue line MBTA access.', 'You are 1 block to Piers Park for some of the finest views of the skyline.', 'Multiple restaurants and nightlife destinations are walkable including Tall Ships, Cunard Tavern, Reel House & the ICA.', 'Pets considered.', 'September 1st', 'FEATURES', 'Close to park', 'Close to public transportation', 'Convenient location', 'Disposal', 'Eat-in Kitchen', 'Granite Counter Tops', 'Hardwood Floors', 'High Ceiling', 'Laundry in Unit', 'Microwave', 'Modern Bath', 'New Appliances', 'New/Renovated Kitchen', 'Resident parking', 'Stainless Steel Appliance(s)']
